#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn22.20"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn22.20:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 22 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 22 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.20:0.2"
msgid "2. Aniccavagga "
msgstr "2. Impermanence "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 20. Sahetuanattasutta → tatiyahetusuttaṃ (bj) | hetu 3 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn22.20:0.3"
msgid "20. Sahetuanattasutta "
msgstr "20. Not-Self With Its Cause "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn22.20:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.20:1.2"
msgid "“Rūpaṃ, bhikkhave, anattā. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, form is not-self. "

msgctxt "sn22.20:1.3"
msgid "Yopi hetu yopi paccayo rūpassa uppādāya, sopi anattā. "
msgstr "The cause and condition that gives rise to form is also not-self. "

msgctxt "sn22.20:1.4"
msgid "Anattasambhūtaṃ, bhikkhave, rūpaṃ kuto attā bhavissati. "
msgstr "Since form is produced by what is not-self, how could it be self? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.20:1.5"
msgid "Vedanā anattā … "
msgstr "Feeling is not-self … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.20:1.6"
msgid "saññā anattā … "
msgstr "Perception is not-self … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.20:1.7"
msgid "saṅkhārā anattā … "
msgstr "Choices are not-self … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.20:1.8"
msgid "viññāṇaṃ anattā. "
msgstr "Consciousness is not-self. "

msgctxt "sn22.20:1.9"
msgid "Yopi hetu yopi paccayo viññāṇassa uppādāya, sopi anattā. "
msgstr "The cause and condition that gives rise to consciousness is also not-self. "

msgctxt "sn22.20:1.10"
msgid "Anattasambhūtaṃ, bhikkhave, viññāṇaṃ kuto attā bhavissati. "
msgstr "Since consciousness is produced by what is not-self, how could it be self? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.20:1.11"
msgid "Evaṃ passaṃ … pe … "
msgstr "Seeing this … "

msgctxt "sn22.20:1.12"
msgid "nāparaṃ itthattāyā’ti pajānātī”ti. "
msgstr "They understand: ‘… there is no return to any state of existence.’” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn22.20:1.13"
msgid "Navamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

